1
00:01:59,789 --> 00:02:00,590
Jin Xi,

2
00:02:01,560 --> 00:02:02,590
don't worry.

3
00:02:03,640 --> 00:02:05,700
I will take good care of Her Highness.

4
00:02:06,640 --> 00:02:07,950
If one day

5
00:02:07,950 --> 00:02:09,680
she is truly unhappy,

6
00:02:10,470 --> 00:02:12,870
I will find a way to
send her back to Changmo.

7
00:02:29,870 --> 00:02:31,360
She's gone.

8
00:02:31,360 --> 00:02:32,690
I'm sorry for your loss.

9
00:02:34,870 --> 00:02:37,430
This might just be Jin Xi's fate.

10
00:02:38,280 --> 00:02:40,280
Jin Xi came to see me before she died.

11
00:02:40,400 --> 00:02:41,360
She told me

12
00:02:42,079 --> 00:02:43,360
to leave the capital,

13
00:02:44,030 --> 00:02:45,030
fearing it would be dangerous.

14
00:02:45,030 --> 00:02:45,800
I know.

15
00:02:46,120 --> 00:02:48,450
Changmo has never given up its ambitions.

16
00:02:48,590 --> 00:02:50,030
As long as the war continues,

17
00:02:50,030 --> 00:02:51,690
the people will have no peace.

18
00:02:52,280 --> 00:02:53,680
We can only wait and see,

19
00:02:54,240 --> 00:02:55,560
and be on our guard.

20
00:02:58,360 --> 00:02:59,120
Drink up.

21
00:02:59,150 --> 00:03:00,880
I have the hangover cure ready.

22
00:03:01,030 --> 00:03:02,840
Let's get drunk tonight.

23
00:03:04,000 --> 00:03:05,910
Then I'll drink first.

24
00:03:10,630 --> 00:03:12,400
If you drink like this,

25
00:03:12,630 --> 00:03:14,760
you'll be the first one drunk tonight.

26
00:03:15,400 --> 00:03:16,680
If I get drunk,

27
00:03:17,280 --> 00:03:18,680
I still have you, don't I?

28
00:03:31,590 --> 00:03:32,870
I don't know why.

29
00:03:33,630 --> 00:03:35,079
We three brothers

30
00:03:35,750 --> 00:03:37,430
used to be so close.

31
00:03:39,079 --> 00:03:40,079
Between us,

32
00:03:40,590 --> 00:03:42,120
what exactly happened?

33
00:03:45,680 --> 00:03:47,280
Things change.

34
00:03:48,840 --> 00:03:50,640
Nothing stays the same forever.

35
00:03:52,150 --> 00:03:53,210
I haven't changed.

36
00:03:54,150 --> 00:03:55,470
Since I was a kid,

37
00:03:55,470 --> 00:03:56,670
I have never changed.

38
00:04:04,590 --> 00:04:05,190
Come on,

39
00:04:05,750 --> 00:04:07,280
have another drink with me.

40
00:04:18,480 --> 00:04:19,920
Slow down.

41
00:04:20,160 --> 00:04:23,240
I haven't fallen
on the battlefield for years.

42
00:04:24,480 --> 00:04:25,870
How could I fall here?

43
00:04:25,870 --> 00:04:27,830
I told you to take the hangover cure,
but you refused.

44
00:04:27,830 --> 00:04:29,040
You are so stubborn.

45
00:04:29,360 --> 00:04:30,510
How did I not know when we were kids

46
00:04:30,510 --> 00:04:31,630
that you talked so much?

47
00:04:31,630 --> 00:04:32,750
What did you say?

48
00:04:34,360 --> 00:04:36,040
Nothing. Hurry home.

49
00:04:38,390 --> 00:04:39,190
Be careful.

50
00:04:41,270 --> 00:04:42,070
This way.

51
00:04:44,630 --> 00:04:45,430
Watch out.

52
00:04:48,270 --> 00:04:49,390
Mm.

53
00:05:44,480 --> 00:05:46,480
We haven't seen each other in years.

54
00:05:47,040 --> 00:05:48,800
You haven't changed at all.

55
00:05:49,630 --> 00:05:50,510
But thankfully,

56
00:05:50,510 --> 00:05:52,600
heaven let you find me again.

57
00:05:54,240 --> 00:05:56,040
You've returned to the capital,

58
00:05:56,070 --> 00:05:57,800
and I've opened a medical hall.

59
00:05:59,070 --> 00:05:59,800
This way,

60
00:06:00,720 --> 00:06:01,800
we will never

61
00:06:01,800 --> 00:06:03,190
be apart again.

62
00:06:16,000 --> 00:06:17,070
Sleep well.

63
00:06:17,630 --> 00:06:18,800
I believe

64
00:06:19,270 --> 00:06:21,390
that every day with you

65
00:06:22,040 --> 00:06:23,630
will be the best day.

66
00:06:40,680 --> 00:06:42,000
Strategist Mo Du,

67
00:06:42,510 --> 00:06:44,270
there is a message
from the King of Changmo.

68
00:06:44,270 --> 00:06:45,630
Said the time has come.

69
00:06:46,270 --> 00:06:47,920
We need to take action.

70
00:06:52,240 --> 00:06:53,830
Understood.

71
00:07:57,680 --> 00:07:59,600
What's wrong?

72
00:07:59,600 --> 00:08:00,190
Wake up.

73
00:08:01,750 --> 00:08:02,750
Here.

74
00:08:04,310 --> 00:08:05,570
What's wrong with you?

75
00:08:06,560 --> 00:08:07,190
Mother.

76
00:08:07,830 --> 00:08:08,390
What's wrong?

77
00:08:08,390 --> 00:08:08,850
Mother.

78
00:08:09,480 --> 00:08:10,240
Mother!

79
00:08:14,680 --> 00:08:15,560
Sit down first.

80
00:08:17,270 --> 00:08:18,070
What's...

81
00:08:20,040 --> 00:08:20,950
Bear with it.

82
00:08:43,360 --> 00:08:44,159
Your Majesty.

83
00:08:44,750 --> 00:08:45,600
An epidemic has spread

84
00:08:45,600 --> 00:08:46,800
throughout Jinglan.

85
00:08:46,870 --> 00:08:48,000
It is highly contagious

86
00:08:48,000 --> 00:08:49,150
and acts fast.

87
00:08:49,270 --> 00:08:50,870
Countless people have died.

88
00:08:50,960 --> 00:08:53,270
If we can't find a cure for the epidemic,

89
00:08:53,480 --> 00:08:55,600
the capital might be...

90
00:08:55,910 --> 00:08:56,910
My ministers,

91
00:08:57,320 --> 00:08:58,840
do you have any good solutions?

92
00:08:58,840 --> 00:09:00,120
What should we do?

93
00:09:08,440 --> 00:09:09,360
Li Shichang.

94
00:09:10,840 --> 00:09:12,030
Your Majesty.

95
00:09:12,030 --> 00:09:13,390
In my opinion,

96
00:09:13,390 --> 00:09:14,270
we must now

97
00:09:14,270 --> 00:09:16,750
abandon these infected citizens.

98
00:09:16,960 --> 00:09:18,630
We should gather them together

99
00:09:18,630 --> 00:09:20,360
and execute them all.

100
00:09:28,030 --> 00:09:28,890
Physician Han.

101
00:09:29,440 --> 00:09:30,960
You have treated an epidemic.

102
00:09:30,960 --> 00:09:32,220
You have also cured me.

103
00:09:32,960 --> 00:09:33,960
Tell me,

104
00:09:34,390 --> 00:09:36,080
what should we do about this disease?

105
00:09:36,080 --> 00:09:37,200
Your Majesty.

106
00:09:37,480 --> 00:09:38,870
I believe

107
00:09:38,870 --> 00:09:40,840
we should quarantine them.

108
00:09:40,840 --> 00:09:41,840
Quarantine?

109
00:09:42,000 --> 00:09:43,480
First, control the spread,

110
00:09:43,480 --> 00:09:44,480
then treat them gradually.

111
00:09:44,480 --> 00:09:46,240
So I beg Your Majesty

112
00:09:46,360 --> 00:09:47,630
to dispatch people as soon as possible

113
00:09:47,630 --> 00:09:49,670
to keep all civilians at home.

114
00:09:49,790 --> 00:09:51,240
Those who are severely ill

115
00:09:51,240 --> 00:09:53,720
should be escorted to the medical hall
by well-protected professionals.

116
00:09:53,720 --> 00:09:55,030
I have already found

117
00:09:55,030 --> 00:09:57,080
the Han family medical manual
left by my father.

118
00:09:57,080 --> 00:09:58,870
I believe I will soon find

119
00:09:58,870 --> 00:09:59,910
the right prescription.

120
00:09:59,910 --> 00:10:00,480
Good.

121
00:10:01,870 --> 00:10:03,600
The remaining troops in the capital

122
00:10:03,600 --> 00:10:05,960
will all be under the unified command
of General Xiao.

123
00:10:05,960 --> 00:10:08,750
Fully cooperate with Physician Han
to treat the patients.

124
00:10:08,750 --> 00:10:10,440
-I receive the decree.
-I receive the decree.

125
00:10:10,440 --> 00:10:12,240
The Imperial Medical Academy
shouldn't stay idle either.

126
00:10:12,240 --> 00:10:13,320
All physicians

127
00:10:13,320 --> 00:10:15,080
must go out and treat the people.

128
00:10:15,080 --> 00:10:16,870
Anyone who makes a contribution

129
00:10:16,870 --> 00:10:18,630
will be heavily rewarded.

130
00:10:18,630 --> 00:10:19,550
Yes.

131
00:10:21,000 --> 00:10:24,200
Report!

132
00:10:25,840 --> 00:10:26,840
Your Majesty.

133
00:10:27,200 --> 00:10:28,750
Tianlang Pass

134
00:10:28,750 --> 00:10:30,440
has fallen.

135
00:10:30,670 --> 00:10:31,960
General Gan Yi of Changmo

136
00:10:31,960 --> 00:10:33,390
is leading hundreds of thousands of troops

137
00:10:33,390 --> 00:10:35,250
and heading towards the capital.

138
00:10:35,870 --> 00:10:37,360
What should we do?

139
00:10:39,150 --> 00:10:40,150
What are we going to do?

140
00:10:40,150 --> 00:10:41,720
How can the capital be safe?

141
00:10:42,670 --> 00:10:43,960
What should we do?

142
00:10:43,960 --> 00:10:45,240
Are they truly invincible?

143
00:10:45,240 --> 00:10:46,480
The capital cannot fall.

144
00:10:46,480 --> 00:10:47,750
Why panic?

145
00:10:48,550 --> 00:10:49,950
It won't fall into chaos.

146
00:10:50,790 --> 00:10:51,600
Dismissed.

147
00:10:52,840 --> 00:10:54,360
We take our leave.

148
00:10:54,360 --> 00:10:55,220
I take my leave.

149
00:11:02,960 --> 00:11:03,870
Xiao Chi.

150
00:11:04,270 --> 00:11:06,360
You have guarded Tianlang Pass for years.

151
00:11:06,360 --> 00:11:07,480
The pass is strong.

152
00:11:08,240 --> 00:11:09,720
Why did the Changmo people

153
00:11:09,870 --> 00:11:12,000
suddenly break through it all at once?

154
00:11:15,390 --> 00:11:16,480
Your Majesty.

155
00:11:16,630 --> 00:11:17,750
Spies reported that

156
00:11:17,750 --> 00:11:18,600
at Tianlang Pass,

157
00:11:18,600 --> 00:11:19,600
half the soldiers

158
00:11:19,630 --> 00:11:20,430
and civilians

159
00:11:20,670 --> 00:11:21,600
have fallen ill.

160
00:11:21,670 --> 00:11:24,800
And this time, Changmo
attacked with their entire army.

161
00:11:24,870 --> 00:11:26,750
Even the strongest walls

162
00:11:26,750 --> 00:11:28,280
would be hard to withstand.

163
00:11:31,000 --> 00:11:33,080
It was I who summoned you back.

164
00:11:33,630 --> 00:11:35,240
It seems it's my fault.

165
00:11:37,960 --> 00:11:39,240
I never meant that.

166
00:11:40,240 --> 00:11:41,030
Chi.

167
00:11:41,750 --> 00:11:43,960
Changmo is about to attack the capital.

168
00:11:44,550 --> 00:11:45,960
Do you have any countermeasures?

169
00:11:45,960 --> 00:11:46,840
Your Majesty.

170
00:11:47,480 --> 00:11:50,240
Many soldiers and civilians
in the capital are also infected.

171
00:11:50,240 --> 00:11:52,960
Physician Han and I will find
a solution as soon as possible.

172
00:11:52,960 --> 00:11:54,480
I will gather all our forces,

173
00:11:54,480 --> 00:11:56,270
and rely on the walls of the capital,

174
00:11:56,270 --> 00:11:59,800
to fight a decisive battle
with Changmo's army under the walls.

175
00:12:00,870 --> 00:12:02,200
Defending?

176
00:12:04,480 --> 00:12:06,140
Do we have a chance of winning?

177
00:12:06,870 --> 00:12:07,790
This plague

178
00:12:08,550 --> 00:12:10,150
should be the work of Changmo.

179
00:12:10,150 --> 00:12:11,840
They came prepared this time.

180
00:12:12,080 --> 00:12:13,200
And our Jinglan

181
00:12:13,200 --> 00:12:14,870
is now troubled by disease from within.

182
00:12:14,870 --> 00:12:15,630
Defending

183
00:12:16,750 --> 00:12:18,080
is also our only option.

184
00:12:18,390 --> 00:12:19,990
As for the chance of winning,

185
00:12:21,360 --> 00:12:23,000
I will certainly do my best.

186
00:12:23,150 --> 00:12:25,010
It seems that this is the only way.

187
00:12:25,240 --> 00:12:27,480
The people in the city are in a panic now.

188
00:12:27,840 --> 00:12:29,790
And that useless Li Shichang,

189
00:12:30,630 --> 00:12:32,890
he wants to kill all the infected people.

190
00:12:33,000 --> 00:12:34,600
If it goes well, that's fine.

191
00:12:34,870 --> 00:12:35,670
Otherwise,

192
00:12:35,960 --> 00:12:37,760
it will cause another uprising.

193
00:12:38,000 --> 00:12:39,080
Your Majesty.

194
00:12:39,390 --> 00:12:40,450
I speak out of turn,

195
00:12:40,600 --> 00:12:41,480
but his advice

196
00:12:41,670 --> 00:12:43,070
is indeed unacceptable.

197
00:12:43,080 --> 00:12:45,010
The lives of the people matter too.

198
00:12:45,240 --> 00:12:46,670
How could such words come from

199
00:12:46,670 --> 00:12:48,670
a court minister?

200
00:12:49,630 --> 00:12:51,030
Thinking back to when my father

201
00:12:51,030 --> 00:12:53,270
served the court with such a person,

202
00:12:53,840 --> 00:12:55,770
it's no wonder our home was raided.

203
00:12:58,480 --> 00:13:00,410
The Han family's case back then...

204
00:13:02,200 --> 00:13:04,600
The Han family's case has been cleared up.

205
00:13:05,080 --> 00:13:06,870
There was indeed

206
00:13:06,870 --> 00:13:09,200
an extra strong dose in the prescription.

207
00:13:10,240 --> 00:13:12,300
I also know a bit about what happened.

208
00:13:12,670 --> 00:13:15,240
Many soldiers and commoners died.

209
00:13:16,240 --> 00:13:17,360
On his deathbed, my father

210
00:13:17,360 --> 00:13:19,030
held my hand and told me,

211
00:13:19,480 --> 00:13:20,240
back then,

212
00:13:20,750 --> 00:13:23,030
the Han family was indeed wronged.

213
00:13:25,390 --> 00:13:26,790
He had no chance anymore.

214
00:13:27,080 --> 00:13:28,480
He urged me,

215
00:13:28,630 --> 00:13:29,960
if I ever had the chance,

216
00:13:30,240 --> 00:13:32,100
I must compensate the Han family.

217
00:13:32,630 --> 00:13:33,270
I will

218
00:13:33,790 --> 00:13:36,050
definitely clear the Han family's name.

219
00:13:36,080 --> 00:13:37,480
Thank you, Your Majesty.

220
00:13:37,670 --> 00:13:40,030
The Han family serves the people.

221
00:13:40,240 --> 00:13:42,360
As long as the people are well,

222
00:13:42,550 --> 00:13:44,210
that is compensation enough.

223
00:13:44,240 --> 00:13:45,200
Of course.

224
00:13:47,360 --> 00:13:48,120
Chi,

225
00:13:48,320 --> 00:13:49,120
sit and speak.

226
00:13:49,150 --> 00:13:50,550
Thank you, Your Majesty.

227
00:13:52,750 --> 00:13:53,750
I was thinking,

228
00:13:54,600 --> 00:13:55,840
if we safely pass

229
00:13:55,840 --> 00:13:57,480
this crisis,

230
00:13:57,630 --> 00:13:59,690
I want to grant a marriage for you two.

231
00:14:03,870 --> 00:14:04,960
Emperor.

232
00:14:09,750 --> 00:14:11,550
I must hurry back and find

233
00:14:11,550 --> 00:14:12,960
a cure for the plague.

234
00:14:12,960 --> 00:14:15,090
I will take my leave now, Your Majesty.

235
00:14:26,030 --> 00:14:27,200
I will withdraw now.

236
00:14:40,390 --> 00:14:41,200
Your Majesty.

237
00:14:47,600 --> 00:14:48,270
Chu.

238
00:14:48,270 --> 00:14:49,630
About Fei Zheng,

239
00:14:49,630 --> 00:14:50,690
I have my own plans.

240
00:14:51,790 --> 00:14:53,120
You don't need to worry.

241
00:14:53,670 --> 00:14:54,730
Yes, Your Majesty.

242
00:15:01,200 --> 00:15:02,660
Greetings, Consort Ling.

243
00:15:05,270 --> 00:15:06,240
Your Majesty.

244
00:15:07,670 --> 00:15:08,670
Why are you here?

245
00:15:09,840 --> 00:15:11,200
Didn't I tell you to stay in the palace

246
00:15:11,200 --> 00:15:12,960
and rest for the baby?

247
00:15:13,360 --> 00:15:14,560
Why won't you listen?

248
00:15:17,960 --> 00:15:19,670
Eat something.

249
00:15:27,030 --> 00:15:28,080
General Xiao.

250
00:15:28,390 --> 00:15:29,520
Yes, Your Highness.

251
00:15:29,550 --> 00:15:30,790
The Changmo army

252
00:15:32,440 --> 00:15:34,500
has reached the gates of the capital?

253
00:15:34,510 --> 00:15:35,870
Your father misses you?

254
00:15:36,670 --> 00:15:38,960
If he missed you,
he should've just come to see you.

255
00:15:38,960 --> 00:15:40,960
Why did he bring so many people?

256
00:15:41,550 --> 00:15:42,600
But don't worry.

257
00:15:42,840 --> 00:15:44,150
As long as Chi is here,

258
00:15:44,790 --> 00:15:46,750
no matter how many people he brings,

259
00:15:46,750 --> 00:15:48,870
he won't take you away from me.

260
00:15:49,960 --> 00:15:51,030
If the Changmo army

261
00:15:51,030 --> 00:15:52,750
really reaches the city walls,

262
00:15:52,750 --> 00:15:53,870
let me out.

263
00:15:54,030 --> 00:15:55,030
I will talk to them,

264
00:15:55,030 --> 00:15:56,200
and they will definitely retreat.

265
00:15:56,200 --> 00:15:57,000
Impossible.

266
00:15:57,870 --> 00:15:58,960
If you never come back,

267
00:15:58,960 --> 00:15:59,760
what will I do?

268
00:16:00,030 --> 00:16:01,120
You are still carrying

269
00:16:01,120 --> 00:16:02,920
the royal bloodline of Jinglan.

270
00:16:03,240 --> 00:16:04,120
If

271
00:16:04,440 --> 00:16:05,390
they use you

272
00:16:05,390 --> 00:16:07,190
and my bloodline to threaten me,

273
00:16:07,840 --> 00:16:08,870
would I have no choice but

274
00:16:08,870 --> 00:16:10,530
to surrender the entire city?

275
00:16:10,750 --> 00:16:12,030
They wouldn't do that.

276
00:16:15,870 --> 00:16:16,670
Your Majesty,

277
00:16:17,240 --> 00:16:19,030
I will take my leave now.

278
00:16:22,200 --> 00:16:24,360
Keep the civilians
in the city under control

279
00:16:24,360 --> 00:16:26,490
and train the existing soldiers well.

280
00:16:26,630 --> 00:16:27,080
Yes.

281
00:16:27,440 --> 00:16:29,040
Rest assured, Your Majesty.

282
00:16:34,840 --> 00:16:36,700
Who allowed you to act on your own?

283
00:16:37,550 --> 00:16:39,320
I just wanted to come see you.

284
00:16:39,360 --> 00:16:40,270
For what?

285
00:16:40,790 --> 00:16:41,910
See if I'm dead?

286
00:16:42,840 --> 00:16:44,240
If I die,

287
00:16:44,480 --> 00:16:45,270
you can just tell them

288
00:16:45,270 --> 00:16:47,120
to open the gates and surrender, right?

289
00:16:47,120 --> 00:16:48,850
Then you can go back to Changmo.

290
00:16:49,030 --> 00:16:50,200
No, Your Majesty.

291
00:16:50,670 --> 00:16:51,870
That's not what I meant.

292
00:16:51,870 --> 00:16:53,470
Then what were you thinking?

293
00:16:54,480 --> 00:16:56,790
I killed your dowry maid,

294
00:16:57,390 --> 00:16:59,200
so you came to question me?

295
00:17:00,000 --> 00:17:01,000
Jin Xi...

296
00:17:02,550 --> 00:17:04,310
Was she really a spy?

297
00:17:05,400 --> 00:17:06,790
She came with you,

298
00:17:07,640 --> 00:17:09,640
yet you don't know who she really is?

299
00:17:09,829 --> 00:17:10,880
I didn't know.

300
00:17:12,829 --> 00:17:15,030
I am not someone who kills the innocent.

301
00:17:15,480 --> 00:17:17,210
If she wasn't trying to kill me,

302
00:17:17,270 --> 00:17:18,960
she wouldn't have died.

303
00:17:19,550 --> 00:17:21,030
But you killed her.

304
00:17:21,790 --> 00:17:23,880
I am all alone in this palace now.

305
00:17:23,880 --> 00:17:25,310
Have I not sent enough palace maids

306
00:17:25,310 --> 00:17:26,240
to serve you?

307
00:17:26,240 --> 00:17:28,240
Jin Xi grew up with me.

308
00:17:28,590 --> 00:17:30,400
She came all the way from Changmo

309
00:17:30,400 --> 00:17:31,480
to accompany me in my marriage.

310
00:17:31,480 --> 00:17:32,810
But she tried to kill me!

311
00:17:37,000 --> 00:17:37,750
Your Changmo has already

312
00:17:37,750 --> 00:17:39,310
broken through Tianlang Pass.

313
00:17:39,310 --> 00:17:41,370
They are about to attack the capital.

314
00:17:41,880 --> 00:17:43,830
Should I keep 2 spies by my side?

315
00:17:44,830 --> 00:17:46,240
What are you thinking?

316
00:17:46,880 --> 00:17:47,640
Fine.

317
00:17:48,550 --> 00:17:49,480
I'll assume you didn't know

318
00:17:49,480 --> 00:17:50,510
about Jin Xi.

319
00:17:51,640 --> 00:17:52,640
I don't blame you.

320
00:17:54,680 --> 00:17:55,790
Then just

321
00:17:57,790 --> 00:17:59,790
protect our child well.

322
00:18:03,160 --> 00:18:04,360
Don't come out again.

323
00:18:05,350 --> 00:18:06,440
When I have time,

324
00:18:07,920 --> 00:18:08,850
I will go see you.

325
00:18:27,590 --> 00:18:28,240
Chengfeng.

326
00:18:28,240 --> 00:18:28,830
Yeah?

327
00:18:29,110 --> 00:18:30,710
What are you thinking about?

328
00:18:32,400 --> 00:18:34,260
I'm not thinking about anything.

329
00:18:34,400 --> 00:18:35,550
Maybe

330
00:18:35,550 --> 00:18:37,030
I didn't sleep well last night,

331
00:18:37,030 --> 00:18:38,400
so I'm a bit sleepy.

332
00:18:41,960 --> 00:18:42,750
Chengfeng,

333
00:18:42,750 --> 00:18:43,030
I'm worried...

334
00:18:43,030 --> 00:18:43,880
What are you worried about?

335
00:18:43,880 --> 00:18:45,740
Are you worried that we can't win?

336
00:18:46,440 --> 00:18:47,270
Let me ask you,

337
00:18:47,480 --> 00:18:49,030
how are your husband's skills?

338
00:18:49,030 --> 00:18:49,720
Very good.

339
00:18:49,720 --> 00:18:51,050
What about the general?

340
00:18:51,160 --> 00:18:52,070
Needless to say.

341
00:18:52,070 --> 00:18:53,240
There you go.

342
00:18:53,240 --> 00:18:55,240
The general has never lost a battle.

343
00:18:55,480 --> 00:18:56,680
With the general's bravery,

344
00:18:56,680 --> 00:18:58,030
he will win every battle.

345
00:18:58,030 --> 00:18:59,480
You don't need to worry.

346
00:18:59,750 --> 00:19:00,680
My child.

347
00:19:00,790 --> 00:19:01,270
Father.

348
00:19:01,270 --> 00:19:01,880
Okay.

349
00:19:01,880 --> 00:19:03,540
I'm going to the battlefield.

350
00:19:03,640 --> 00:19:04,960
You must take care of yourself.

351
00:19:04,960 --> 00:19:05,590
Okay.

352
00:19:06,590 --> 00:19:07,640
I'm leaving.

353
00:19:08,030 --> 00:19:09,920
Take good care of yourself.

354
00:19:09,920 --> 00:19:10,550
Okay.

355
00:19:12,830 --> 00:19:14,310
Let me bow to you.

356
00:19:14,310 --> 00:19:15,640
Okay.

357
00:19:21,030 --> 00:19:22,090
Take care, Father.

358
00:19:22,790 --> 00:19:25,000
Take care of yourself too.

359
00:19:46,640 --> 00:19:47,790
You're here.

360
00:19:48,000 --> 00:19:49,460
The whole city is on alert.

361
00:19:51,030 --> 00:19:53,160
Has the prescription been developed?

362
00:19:55,000 --> 00:19:56,600
It's been developed, right?

363
00:19:59,270 --> 00:20:01,200
Then I will find some patients.

364
00:20:05,480 --> 00:20:06,270
Yunling.

365
00:20:08,480 --> 00:20:09,270
Yunling!

366
00:20:27,880 --> 00:20:28,680
Yunling.

367
00:20:29,640 --> 00:20:30,640
How do you feel?

368
00:20:32,680 --> 00:20:33,480
Come.

369
00:20:35,480 --> 00:20:36,270
How are you?

370
00:20:37,440 --> 00:20:39,440
I found a way to cure the plague.

371
00:20:40,000 --> 00:20:41,880
Halving the dose of red arsenic

372
00:20:42,000 --> 00:20:43,720
will make it safe.

373
00:20:45,200 --> 00:20:46,600
You tested the medicine?

374
00:20:47,270 --> 00:20:47,960
If something happens to you,

375
00:20:47,960 --> 00:20:49,070
what will the people do?

376
00:20:49,070 --> 00:20:49,550
I...

377
00:20:51,640 --> 00:20:52,440
Promise me

378
00:20:53,030 --> 00:20:54,360
you won't do this again.

379
00:20:57,110 --> 00:20:57,920
Okay.

380
00:21:19,110 --> 00:21:20,480
Han's medical prescription.

381
00:21:20,480 --> 00:21:21,880
Three times a day.

382
00:21:22,200 --> 00:21:23,640
Simmer gently.

383
00:21:23,640 --> 00:21:25,110
Immediate relief.

384
00:21:26,030 --> 00:21:27,270
Han's medical prescription.

385
00:21:27,270 --> 00:21:28,720
Three times a day.

386
00:21:29,000 --> 00:21:30,270
Simmer gently.

387
00:21:30,350 --> 00:21:31,960
Immediate relief.

388
00:21:32,440 --> 00:21:34,070
Simmer gently.

389
00:21:40,030 --> 00:21:40,720
Mother,

390
00:21:40,960 --> 00:21:41,350
here.

391
00:22:09,640 --> 00:22:10,440
Thank you.

392
00:22:11,400 --> 00:22:13,720
We're saved.

393
00:22:13,720 --> 00:22:16,640
The lockdown in the capital is lifted.

394
00:22:16,640 --> 00:22:19,000
It's lifted.

395
00:22:19,000 --> 00:22:21,680
The lockdown in the capital is lifted.

396
00:22:21,790 --> 00:22:23,790
The epidemic has been resolved.

397
00:22:23,790 --> 00:22:25,640
The people are mostly unharmed.

398
00:22:25,640 --> 00:22:28,030
It's all thanks to
Your Majesty's blessing.

399
00:22:28,030 --> 00:22:29,400
Then they really

400
00:22:29,720 --> 00:22:31,550
deserve a great reward.

401
00:22:31,790 --> 00:22:33,050
Where are General Xiao

402
00:22:33,750 --> 00:22:34,960
and Physician Han?

403
00:22:35,030 --> 00:22:36,200
Your Majesty,

404
00:22:36,440 --> 00:22:37,750
Physician Han is still treating

405
00:22:37,750 --> 00:22:40,030
the sick elderly, women, and children.

406
00:22:40,350 --> 00:22:41,510
What about Xiao Chi?

407
00:22:42,200 --> 00:22:45,000
Report!

408
00:22:47,270 --> 00:22:48,160
Your Majesty,

409
00:22:48,400 --> 00:22:50,730
the Changmo army has reached the capital.

410
00:22:50,880 --> 00:22:54,960
General Xiao has led
his men out to meet the enemy.

411
00:22:55,680 --> 00:22:57,270
What should we do?

412
00:23:03,030 --> 00:23:04,440
Where is Xiao Chi?

413
00:23:04,440 --> 00:23:06,640
Did he hide because he's afraid?

414
00:23:07,070 --> 00:23:09,160
Tell him to come down and fight me.

415
00:23:09,200 --> 00:23:10,200
To deal with you,

416
00:23:10,200 --> 00:23:11,640
I am more than enough.

417
00:23:11,680 --> 00:23:13,160
No need for our general.

418
00:23:13,160 --> 00:23:14,270
A mere foot soldier

419
00:23:14,270 --> 00:23:15,790
dares to talk big.

420
00:23:15,790 --> 00:23:17,200
You are not my match.

421
00:23:17,270 --> 00:23:19,270
Tell Xiao Chi to come down.

422
00:23:19,270 --> 00:23:20,640
Ignorant fool.

423
00:23:20,640 --> 00:23:21,440
Take this!

424
00:24:20,880 --> 00:24:21,640
Chengfeng!

425
00:24:25,640 --> 00:24:26,440
Chengfeng!

426
00:24:28,590 --> 00:24:29,110
Who...

427
00:24:29,440 --> 00:24:30,500
Who shot the arrow?

428
00:24:31,960 --> 00:24:32,960
It was you.

429
00:24:32,960 --> 00:24:33,640
Meng Ling.

430
00:24:34,680 --> 00:24:36,640
Deploying troops without authorization
is a capital offense.

431
00:24:36,640 --> 00:24:38,640
I just wanted to meet Xiao Chi first.

432
00:24:39,440 --> 00:24:40,240
Gan Yi.

433
00:24:41,400 --> 00:24:42,480
King of Changmo said

434
00:24:42,480 --> 00:24:46,280
he wants to witness the very moment
this city falls with his own eyes.

435
00:24:49,400 --> 00:24:50,720
Gan Yi!

436
00:24:52,960 --> 00:24:53,750
Chengfeng.

437
00:24:56,640 --> 00:24:58,030
Guards!

438
00:25:00,160 --> 00:25:01,070
Retreat!

439
00:25:13,640 --> 00:25:15,030
So...

440
00:25:15,030 --> 00:25:16,830
So what should we do now?

441
00:25:20,680 --> 00:25:22,640
Say something!

442
00:25:26,200 --> 00:25:27,310
Your Majesty.

443
00:25:28,200 --> 00:25:30,070
In my opinion,

444
00:25:30,070 --> 00:25:32,200
there is only one way.

445
00:25:32,200 --> 00:25:33,200
Speak!

446
00:25:35,030 --> 00:25:36,680
Open the city gates

447
00:25:37,550 --> 00:25:38,200
and

448
00:25:38,720 --> 00:25:40,550
surrender.

449
00:25:41,200 --> 00:25:42,160
This is

450
00:25:42,160 --> 00:25:43,400
the only way.

451
00:25:43,400 --> 00:25:44,270
Li Shichang.

452
00:25:45,200 --> 00:25:47,350
As a Chief Minister,

453
00:25:47,640 --> 00:25:49,680
you are advising me to surrender?

454
00:25:51,000 --> 00:25:52,590
Li Shichang!

455
00:25:55,160 --> 00:25:56,590
Your Majesty.

456
00:25:57,480 --> 00:25:58,440
This is

457
00:25:58,830 --> 00:26:00,960
the best way,

458
00:26:01,350 --> 00:26:03,480
and the only choice.

459
00:26:05,200 --> 00:26:06,830
Only then

460
00:26:08,880 --> 00:26:10,200
can you and the others

461
00:26:10,960 --> 00:26:11,640
safely

462
00:26:12,070 --> 00:26:13,590
survive.

463
00:26:13,590 --> 00:26:15,440
I am the Emperor.

464
00:26:16,070 --> 00:26:19,030
How can I be the ruler
who loses his kingdom?

465
00:26:25,070 --> 00:26:25,720
Poison!

466
00:26:26,270 --> 00:26:26,880
Lord Li.

467
00:26:27,200 --> 00:26:28,880
Lord Li.

468
00:26:28,880 --> 00:26:30,550
What's wrong with Lord Li?

469
00:26:32,000 --> 00:26:33,440
This is Changmo's Gu poison.

470
00:26:33,440 --> 00:26:35,920
It seems you've been controlled
by the people of Changmo.

471
00:26:35,920 --> 00:26:36,880
Guards!

472
00:26:50,200 --> 00:26:51,960
Your Majesty...

473
00:27:13,400 --> 00:27:16,640
This is the consequence
of colluding with the enemy.

474
00:27:21,270 --> 00:27:23,350
Everyone who betrayed me

475
00:27:23,960 --> 00:27:25,720
and acts as a spy

476
00:27:26,070 --> 00:27:28,440
must die!

477
00:27:41,270 --> 00:27:42,070
Yunling.

478
00:27:43,640 --> 00:27:44,550
Uncle Lie.

479
00:27:46,880 --> 00:27:48,410
Why are you here, Uncle Lie?

480
00:27:48,480 --> 00:27:49,810
I missed you, of course.

481
00:27:50,240 --> 00:27:51,350
It's been a while.

482
00:27:51,480 --> 00:27:53,740
Your medical hall is running quite well.

483
00:27:54,030 --> 00:27:55,830
Xiao Chi knows I like these,

484
00:27:55,830 --> 00:27:57,440
so he sent a lot of herbs.

485
00:27:58,750 --> 00:28:00,240
Come back to Changmo with me.

486
00:28:00,240 --> 00:28:02,440
Tomorrow, the Changmo army
will breach this place.

487
00:28:02,440 --> 00:28:04,300
It will soon become a living hell.

488
00:28:04,880 --> 00:28:05,640
Uncle Lie.

489
00:28:06,270 --> 00:28:07,640
I trust Xiao Chi.

490
00:28:07,750 --> 00:28:09,350
He will definitely defend Jinglan

491
00:28:09,350 --> 00:28:11,010
and survive against all odds.

492
00:28:11,030 --> 00:28:12,350
Defend Jinglan?

493
00:28:13,480 --> 00:28:15,610
You're still thinking about Jinglan.

494
00:28:15,880 --> 00:28:18,680
Have you forgotten
how your father died back then?

495
00:28:18,880 --> 00:28:20,640
Have you forgotten how I
narrowly escaped death

496
00:28:20,640 --> 00:28:21,830
to rescue you from the Jinglan Kingdom?

497
00:28:21,830 --> 00:28:22,480
Uncle Lie.

498
00:28:22,480 --> 00:28:23,400
Listen to me.

499
00:28:24,160 --> 00:28:25,550
For the Emperor,

500
00:28:25,550 --> 00:28:27,160
the civil and military officials,
and the commoners,

501
00:28:27,160 --> 00:28:28,590
how many patients did our Han family save?

502
00:28:28,590 --> 00:28:29,640
But what did they do?

503
00:28:29,640 --> 00:28:31,440
Just because of my tiny mistake,

504
00:28:31,440 --> 00:28:32,640
they wiped out our Han family

505
00:28:32,640 --> 00:28:33,480
and executed everyone.

506
00:28:33,480 --> 00:28:35,210
Have you forgotten all of this?

507
00:28:35,480 --> 00:28:36,960
Your mistake?

508
00:28:49,200 --> 00:28:52,240
Were those potent ingredients
on the prescription

509
00:28:53,550 --> 00:28:55,070
added by you?

510
00:29:01,680 --> 00:29:02,750
Uncle Lie,

511
00:29:02,750 --> 00:29:04,350
why did you do that?

512
00:29:05,030 --> 00:29:06,310
Do you know how many people

513
00:29:06,310 --> 00:29:07,880
that prescription killed back then?

514
00:29:07,880 --> 00:29:09,480
Lord Zhang's son died tragically,

515
00:29:09,480 --> 00:29:11,000
that's why he targeted our Han family

516
00:29:11,000 --> 00:29:12,640
and tortured Mo so much.

517
00:29:13,030 --> 00:29:14,550
Because of that prescription,

518
00:29:14,550 --> 00:29:16,200
our Han family was wiped out.

519
00:29:16,200 --> 00:29:17,680
Why on earth did you do that?

520
00:29:17,680 --> 00:29:19,200
I did it for your father.

521
00:29:19,270 --> 00:29:20,550
The prescription your father developed

522
00:29:20,550 --> 00:29:22,640
had very little effect on that plague.

523
00:29:22,640 --> 00:29:23,680
To help him,

524
00:29:23,680 --> 00:29:25,480
I added a few strong medicines to it.

525
00:29:25,480 --> 00:29:26,880
If it succeeded,

526
00:29:26,960 --> 00:29:28,790
not only could we save many patients,

527
00:29:28,790 --> 00:29:29,880
but our Han family

528
00:29:29,880 --> 00:29:31,880
would also achieve infinite glory.

529
00:29:35,070 --> 00:29:36,870
But things didn't go as planned.

530
00:29:36,880 --> 00:29:38,410
None of it matters anymore.

531
00:29:38,590 --> 00:29:39,750
It's all in the past.

532
00:29:40,070 --> 00:29:40,960
Back then, your father covered

533
00:29:40,960 --> 00:29:42,200
for the mess I made.

534
00:29:42,640 --> 00:29:44,240
So I will get revenge

535
00:29:45,480 --> 00:29:47,400
for the Han family.

536
00:29:47,680 --> 00:29:48,550
Do you know?

537
00:29:48,880 --> 00:29:50,270
After this plague,

538
00:29:51,070 --> 00:29:54,030
Jinglan is a spent force.

539
00:29:54,030 --> 00:29:56,490
It will soon be defeated
by the Changmo army.

540
00:29:57,070 --> 00:29:57,880
Really.

541
00:29:58,680 --> 00:30:00,310
Don’t tell me this epidemic

542
00:30:01,310 --> 00:30:02,960
is also your doing.

543
00:30:05,550 --> 00:30:06,400
It is.

544
00:30:10,750 --> 00:30:13,440
Uncle Lie, you want to
avenge our Han family.

545
00:30:14,720 --> 00:30:15,880
It was you.

546
00:30:16,110 --> 00:30:17,480
You killed my father.

547
00:30:17,480 --> 00:30:19,160
You doomed the whole Han family.

548
00:30:19,160 --> 00:30:21,160
You are not just a sinner
to the Han family.

549
00:30:21,160 --> 00:30:23,090
You are a sinner to the whole world.

550
00:30:29,200 --> 00:30:30,030
Leave.

551
00:30:30,480 --> 00:30:31,640
Go back to your Changmo.

552
00:30:31,640 --> 00:30:33,440
Even if the city falls tomorrow,

553
00:30:33,790 --> 00:30:34,880
I won't leave.

554
00:30:37,270 --> 00:30:38,790
No matter how many people died,

555
00:30:38,790 --> 00:30:40,920
I am taking revenge for our Han family.

556
00:30:41,440 --> 00:30:43,300
I am not a sinner of our Han family.

557
00:30:46,110 --> 00:30:47,510
I believe

558
00:30:48,440 --> 00:30:51,370
I will definitely become
the glory of the Han family.

559
00:31:00,240 --> 00:31:01,640
Mo has woken up.

560
00:31:02,160 --> 00:31:03,400
He keeps asking me

561
00:31:03,830 --> 00:31:05,440
when he can see

562
00:31:05,440 --> 00:31:07,370
his cousin he misses day and night.

563
00:31:08,640 --> 00:31:10,100
I'll ask you one last time.

564
00:31:10,830 --> 00:31:12,350
Go back to Changmo with me.

565
00:31:12,640 --> 00:31:14,440
Mo will always be my cousin.

566
00:31:14,640 --> 00:31:15,640
And you...

567
00:31:16,880 --> 00:31:18,440
A ruthless person like you

568
00:31:18,440 --> 00:31:19,680
has no place in the Han family.
